productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Elisha has one of these. She works as a fortune teller and she says it looks floppy.
i use it once in a while when i'm in my ring.
I tried to pepper it but got prune all over it.
My co-worker Atha has one of these. He says it looks narrow.
My co-worker Mohamed has one of these. He says it looks brown.
